articles.author: Raya Jalabi
articles.title: Middle East countries move to ban Barbie movie over LGBT+ content - Financial Times
articles.description: Kuwait refuses to show blockbuster film that has broken studio records around the world
articles.content:
Cinemagoers in parts of the Middle East will have to wait a little longer to watch Barbie, Greta Gerwigs pink-hued blockbuster about the iconic Mattel toy.
